          "tz": 480
        },
        "subject": "LU-11847 pcc: Add statistics for PCC",
        "message": "LU-11847 pcc: Add statistics for PCC\n\nTo evaluate the PCC prefetching and evicting algorithm, we need to\nadd statistics for PCC operations to calculate the Byte Hit Rate\n(BHR) and File Hit Rate (FHR).\nThe following statistics for PCC on each client are added in\nllite.*.stats:\nLPROC_LL_PCC_READ_BYTES         \"pcc_read_bytes\"\nLPROC_LL_PCC_WRITE_BYTES        \"pcc_write_bytes\"\nLPROC_LL_PCC_ATTACH             \"pcc_attach_bytes\"\nLRPOC_LL_PCC_RESTORE            \"pcc_restore_bytes\"\nLPROC_LL_PCC_DETACH             \"pcc_detach\"\nLRPOC_LL_PCC_OPEN               \"pcc_open\"\n\nSigned-off-by: Qian Yingjin <qian@ddn.com>\nChange-Id: I2b8e0843a3ee50056c4922ce27f965ded0091129\n"
      },
      "branch": "refs/heads/pcc"
    }
  },
